Package: CenSoloLTR
Type: Package
Title: Genome-Centered SoloLTR Annotation Pipeline for Centromere Regions
Version: 1.1.0
Date: 2026-06-16
Authors@R: c(
    person("User", "Liurxx", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "liurxx@example.com"))
Description: An integrated bioinformatics pipeline for de novo LTR
    retrotransposon annotation, soloLTR detection, and centromere/pericentromere
    region analysis. Starting from a genome FASTA file and centromere BED file,
    the pipeline runs LTR_FINDER, LTR_HARVEST, LTR_retriever, TEsorter, CD-HIT,
    and BLAST to produce comprehensive soloLTR classification, deep annotation
    of CEN/Peri-CEN regions, FASTA sequence extraction, and publication-ready
    stacked bar plots of LTR family composition.
